                           (@comm_ring.add_left_inv _ Œ≥‚ÇÅ a) 
     ... = -(f a) + 0 : by rwr hom_str.map_zero                                                                                              
     ... = -(f a) : @comm_ring.add_zero _ Œ≥‚ÇÇ (-(f a))   

